history.content:
Statistics graduate students will be available on Zoom to chat about graduate school in statistics or anything else that you would want to talk about. Get to know various graduate students other than your GSI's through these office hours and use them to your advantage to get more perspectives on your plan in life!

The office hours will be happening on:

October 23, Friday - 11:30 AM - 12:30 PM
October 28, Wednesday - 12:30 PM - 1:30 PM
November 11, Wednesday - 12:30 PM - 1:30 PM
November 20, Friday - 11:30 AM - 12:30 PM
December 4, Wednesday - 12:30 PM - 1:30 PM

These office hours will be hosted on Zoom: https://berkeley.zoom.us/j/94257558853?pwd=clR0NG9MVnVRRGp4UTFybnRCQmFJZz09 

More info on: https://susa.berkeley.edu/sgup
